61
00:05:32,233 --> 00:05:34,267
<i>It's that man.</i>

62
00:05:44,867 --> 00:05:47,733
Please transfer ownership of Kang Hee to me.

63
00:05:48,300 --> 00:05:50,733
I will take responsibility.

64
00:05:54,833 --> 00:05:56,633
No.

65
